00:56:24,880 --> 00:56:28,020
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}I saw them! I saw them!

675
00:56:28,080 --> 00:56:30,120
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}They're in the town hall!

676
00:56:31,350 --> 00:56:36,860
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Cry "Havoc," and let slip the dogs of war!

